sentences: Radmila "Rada" Manojlović (Serbian Cyrillic: Радмила "Рада" Манојловић, pronounced [ˌrǎdmila maˈnǒːjloʋit͜ɕ]; born 25 August 1985) is a Serbian pop-folk singer.
Additionally, in 2016, she became a judge of the children's version of Zvezde Granda, called Neki novi klinci.
Over the years, Manojlović also received a lot of media attention due to her private life.
She dated fellow Zvezde Granda contestant Milan Stanković between 2008 and 2012.
After that, Manojlović was in a prominent relationship with basketball manager, Momir Gajić, until 2015.
She began dating the winner of the ninth series of Zvezde Granda, Haris Berković, in 2016.
